nodes.text: Executor was a rank of the Yuuzhan Vong Intendant caste. Executors handled various day to day measures, and also managed valuable "living resources"—slaves, Workers, and Shamed Ones. They were also sent out as spies and advance scouts.
Nom Anor and Eshin Worr held the rank. Another executor was on Bonadan negotiating with Lounha in 26 ABY.
